                                            (
                                            @SwingDataViewer.Services.DistanceFunction.Abstract(Model.ThisMonth.TotalDistance[i].Value)
                                            )
                                        </span>
                                    </td>
                                </tr>
                            }
                        </tbody>
                    </table>
                </div>
            </div>

            <div class="card mb-2">
                <div class="card-header">
                    <span class="comment">弾幕薄いよ！何やってんの！？</span>
